   "source": [
    "# Histogram Equalization"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 12,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import cv2\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 30,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def calCumSum(arr: np.array) -> np.ndarray:\n",
    "    cum_sum = np.zeros_like(arr)\n",
    "    cum_sum[0] = arr[0]\n",
    "    arr_len = len(arr)\n",
    "    for idx in range(1, arr_len):\n",
    "        cum_sum[idx] = arr[idx] + cum_sum[idx - 1]\n",
    "\n",
    "    return cum_sum"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def histEq(img: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n",
    "    hist = calHist(img)\n",
    "    cumsum = calCumSum(hist)\n",
    "    cumsum_n = cumsum / cumsum.max()\n",
    "\n",
    "    look_ut = np.zeros(256)\n",
    "    for inten in range(len(cumsum_n)):\n",
    "        new_color = int(np.floor(255 * cumsum_n[inten]))\n",
    "        look_ut[inten] = new_color\n",
    "\n",
    "    new_img = np.zeros_like(img, dtype=np.float)\n",
    "\n",
    "    for old_color, new_color in enumerate(look_ut):\n",
    "        new_img[img == old_color] = new_color\n",
    "    return new_img"
   ]
  },

   "source": [
    "img = cv2.imread('bac_con.png')\n",
    "plt.imshow(img)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"Image Dims: {} X {}\".format(*img.shape))\n",
    "print(\"Max: {}, Min: {}\".format(img.max(), img.min()))\n",
    "print(\"Mean: {:.3f}, Median: {}\".format(img.mean(), np.median(img)))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Image Histogram"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 41,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def calHist(img: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n",
    "    img_flat = img.ravel()\n",
    "    hist = np.zeros(256)\n",
    "\n",
    "    for pix in img_flat:\n",
    "        hist[pix] += 1\n",
    "\n",
    "    return hist\n",
    "\n",
    "# Works faster\n",
    "def calHistFast(img: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n",
    "    img_flat = img.ravel()\n",
    "    hist = np.zeros(256)\n",
    "\n",
    "    for val in range(256):\n",
    "        hist[val] = np.count_nonzero(img==val)\n",
    "\n",
    "    return hist"
   ]
  },

   "source": [
    "def calCumSum(arr: np.array) -> np.ndarray:\n",
    "    cum_sum = np.zeros_like(arr)\n",
    "    cum_sum[0] = arr[0]\n",
    "    arr_len = len(arr)\n",
    "    for idx in range(1, arr_len):\n",
    "        cum_sum[idx] = arr[idx] + cum_sum[idx - 1]\n",
    "    return cum_sum\n"
   ]
